name: First Community Church UCC
directions: We are an open and affirming church. We have both unisex accessible single restrooms and restrooms with stalls labeled by gender that you can use safely according to your gender identity. On Sundays, come to the double glass doors off the parking lot in the back. During the week, come to the front "church office" door. The building is ADA compliant. There is a changing table in the nursery.
comment:
Sundays from 10am-12pm
Office is also open from 9am-3pm Tuesday through Thursday. However, for employee safety, we don't allow anyone unknown in the building unless two or more employees/members are present. Call ahead at 214-823-2117. Also let us know if you need a shower and/or toiletries and snack items.

comment: You must either be attending an event, be a student, or otherwise paying for gym use to use restrooms.
